spec_data.Name: nbdkit-plugin-python-common
spec_data.Description:
This package contains common files shared between Python 2
and Python 3 nbdkit plugins.

You should not install this package directly.  Instead install
either nbdkit-plugin-python2 or nbdkit-plugin-python3.

spec_data.Summary: Python 2 and 3 plugin common files for nbdkit
